{"data":[{"date":"15:38 10/08","title":"MU kh\u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm r\u1ea7m r\u1ed9, Smalling v\u1eabn th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/27/mu-khong-mua-sam-ram-ro-smalling-van-thach-thuc-nhung-doi-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2n binh kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bi-quan-ve-kha-nang-mua-them-nguoi-172-194120.html\" target=\"_blank\">BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</span>.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Chris-Smalling-phat-bieu-ve-MU-truoc-mua-giai-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fred v\u00e0 Dalot. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam duy nh\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Toby Alderweireld, Yerry Mina, Jerome Boateng, Harry Magui, Willian, Ivan Perisic, Sergej Milinkovic-Savic... l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf, nh\u01b0ng BL\u0110 M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, M.U m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chi ra kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i so v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Smalling kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" title=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-18,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling tin M.U v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn, song v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n M.U v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i tin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng M.U b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p do kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng theo t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1eady. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p M.U, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2211","checkdouble":"194177"},{"date":"15:47 10/08","title":"Emery \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA cho Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-emery-phat-bieu-ve-muc-tieu-cua-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, nh\u01b0ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt phong c\u00e1ch.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i t\u1ed1p 4 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, HLV Arsenen Wenger tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal. M\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf ra v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u tham v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh d\u00f9 nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi kh\u00ed ch\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/hlv-emery-phat-bieu-ve-muc-tieu-cua-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a CLB l\u00e0 v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u01a1i v\u00ec c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u\u201d, Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00f9ng nhau c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i cho C\u0110V c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEmery \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal t\u1eeb Wenger. \u00d4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u201cPhong c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng PSG n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sports.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gian, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00ednh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng trong m\u1ed7i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, n\u00f3i lu\u00f4n d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n l\u00e0m. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian, nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ho\u00e0n hi\u1ec7n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dau-la-ban-hop-dong-xuat-sac-nhat-mua-he-2018-172-194147.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal-172-194121.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-chelsea-buon-vui-lan-lon-vu-aaron-ramsey-172-194087.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea bu\u1ed3n vui l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n v\u1ee5 Aaron Ramsey</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-giu-chan-ramsey-vi-chuyen-mon-va-mot-loi-khang-dinh-172-194026.html\">Arsenal gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Ramsey: V\u00ec chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2210","checkdouble":"194178"},{"date":"16:13 10/08","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00e2n binh Fred c\u1ee7a M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sao-tre-khang-dinh-se-giup-do-tan-binh-fred-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eadn may \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi anh khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Th\u00e0nh Chung g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y, Th\u00e0nh Chung \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u1ed7i h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 ngay trong s\u00e1ng nay, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 trong danh s\u00e1ch 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/27/Sep-HAGL-noi-gi-khi-Minh-Vuong-nhan-\u2018ve-vot\u2019-cua-thay-Park-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ea2nh: Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u0103ng.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t: \u201cS\u00e1ng nay, anh L\u00ea Ho\u00e0i Anh \u2013 T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd VFF \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi CLB v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang-seo g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. Hi\u1ec7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh ra H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 bay \u0111i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngay trong chi\u1ec1u nay\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u201cTrong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng may c\u1eadu ta l\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u201d, v\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t t\u1ed1t, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o, \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \"Open Sans\", sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2209","checkdouble":"194180"},{"date":"16:12 10/08","title":"Th\u00eam 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/12/them-1-cau-thu-hagl-duoc-bo-sung-len-tuyen-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e1t ng\u00e0y Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park g\u1ecdi thay th\u1ebf.</h2><h2>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/10/Minh-Vuong-duoc-goi-bo-sung-len-tuyen-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo\u00a0g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a,<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-co-them-ca-chan-thuong-truoc-khi-len-duong-du-asiad-168-194157.html\" target=\"_blank\"> h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u qua 9/8. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay th\u1ebf, v\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a HAGL.</div>\r\n<p>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi \u00f4ng Park ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n, qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ed3m 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n Thanh v\u00e0 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, trong khi s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, h\u00f4m nay (10/8) U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11/8. Theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Pakistan, Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 14, 16 v\u00e0 19/8.\u00a0V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 Nepal v\u00e0 Pakistan \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, O. Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194114.html\">B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o Bola c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)\u00a0<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2208","checkdouble":"194181"},{"date":"16:23 10/08","title":"B\u1ecb nh\u0103m nhe c\u01b0\u1edbp Modric, Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n Inter","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/17/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Luka Modric b\u1ecb Inter Milan ve v\u00e3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Luka Modric t\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 \u0110T Croatia, Inter Milan kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean. H\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f3 ch\u1ed1i t\u1eeb. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Inter s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho Modric m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro, g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111ang l\u0129nh t\u1ea1i Real (6,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro) trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Nerazzurri c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Trung Qu\u1ed1c khi mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Real-Madrid-dam-phan-mua-Mauro-Icardi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Inter mu\u1ed1n Modric c\u1ee7a Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, Real t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a Inter Milan. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi. Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Los Blancos \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Karim Benzema ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t k\u00e9m duy\u00ean. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Icardi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi t\u1edbi 100 b\u00e0n sau 159 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Inter k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Icardi\" title=\"tien dao Icardi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/17/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2017/18, Icardi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh ghi t\u1edbi 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Inter ch\u1ec9 sau 34 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Serie A, \u0111\u1ed3ng Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f9ng Ciro Immobile. \u0110i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Inter l\u00e0 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Icardi trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\">Thibaut Courtois CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-chelsea-muon-duoc-kovacic-tu-real-172-194124.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d Kovacic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-courtois-toi-real-madrid-172-194113.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-muon-giu-chan-luka-modric-180-194111.html\">Real n\u00edu k\u00e9o Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Inter</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-0908-180-194097.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 09/08</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2207","checkdouble":"194183"},{"date":"16:09 10/08","title":"S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/12/sep-hagl-noi-gi-khi-minh-vuong-nhan-ve-vot-cua-thay-park.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eadn may \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi anh khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Th\u00e0nh Chung g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y, Th\u00e0nh Chung \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u1ed7i h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 ngay trong s\u00e1ng nay, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 trong danh s\u00e1ch 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/27/Sep-HAGL-noi-gi-khi-Minh-Vuong-nhan-\u2018ve-vot\u2019-cua-thay-Park-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ea2nh: Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u0103ng.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t: \u201cS\u00e1ng nay, anh L\u00ea Ho\u00e0i Anh \u2013 T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd VFF \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi CLB v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang-seo g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. Hi\u1ec7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh ra H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 bay \u0111i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngay trong chi\u1ec1u nay\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u201cTrong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng may c\u1eadu ta l\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u201d, v\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t t\u1ed1t, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o, \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \"Open Sans\", sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2206","checkdouble":"194186"},{"date":"16:29 10/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhung-van-de-mourinho-can-giai-quyet-truoc-mua-giai-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a H\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m, \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU 2018 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB. Mourinho l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU 2018 Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU 2018 Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/162451-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u1ea7n khai th\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng g\u1ea7n khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho bu\u1ed9c c\u1ef1u sao Juventus ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Matic h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ch\u00ednh m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn gi\u1eefa Pogba v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn M.U t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i so v\u1edbi Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Mourinho ph\u1ea3i khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t&nbsp;\u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay. Pogba \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Mourinho ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf h\u1ebft gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i cho th\u1ea5y anh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 khu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o c\u00e1ch Didier Deschamps s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Pogba \u1edf \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Fred, anh s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Matic t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn th\u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Pogba ch\u01a1i cao h\u01a1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, khi m\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-gap-hoa-them-matic-bo-lo-giai-doan-dau-mua-giai-172-192235.html\" target=\"_blank\">Matic d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span>, Fellaini ho\u1eb7c Herrera c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Anthony Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Sanchez v\u00e0 Rashford. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 23, \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Monaco l\u00e0 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho phai giu bang duoc Martial\" title=\"Mourinho ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAnthony Martial \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng CLB mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n Juventus, Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef Martial \u1edf l\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady \u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Sanchez v\u00e0 Rashford, Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Martial \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Lukaku gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMartial t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tin t\u01b0\u1edfng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t th\u1ee9 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea. Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho can tim ra nhung giai phap huu hieu noi hang thu\" title=\"Mourinho c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay Mourinho v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. \u1ede trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Chris Smalling \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVictor Lindelof v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Phil Jones v\u00e0 Marcos Rojo c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. \u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh, Luke Shaw \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Ashley Young.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, Mourinho s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Matteo Darmian v\u00e0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n khai th\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Dalot, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho Andreas Pereira&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Andreas Pereira th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Granada v\u00e0 Valencia, anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho can trao co hoi nhieu hon cho Andreas Pereira\" title=\"Mourinho c\u1ea7n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho Andreas Pereira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/perrera.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u1ea7n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho Andreas Pereira</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAndreas Pereira kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Khi m\u00e0 Pogba, Herrera v\u00e0 Matic ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, Mourinho c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Pereira \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1t khao ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh, Pereira ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Mourinho \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2205","checkdouble":"194187"},{"date":"16:50 10/08","title":"B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Luka Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/robert-jarni-phat-bieu-ve-real-madrid-va-luka-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Robert Jarni ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Luka Modric. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Modric b\u1ecb Inter ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Anh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p 2-4 song c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Modric v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Inter Milan l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League sau 6 n\u0103m r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 3 n\u0103m li\u1ec1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real. C\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ngu\u1ed3n tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh Modric \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Jarni ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Robert Jarni ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/robert-jarni-phat-bieu-ve-real-madrid-va-luka-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Modric t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRobert Jarni ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Luka Modric. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng 81 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Modric s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ra \u0111i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi Real kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta bi\u1ebft th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\u201d, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Cadena SER. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eb1ng Luka Modric s\u1ebd ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 CLB c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Real-Madrid-dam-phan-mua-Mauro-Icardi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Robert Jarni ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Luka Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, Real \u0111\u00e3 cho ph\u00e9p Mateo Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. V\u1edbi Jarni, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia s\u1ebd thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i CLB Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMateo Kovacic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng song ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n\u201d, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 49 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m song \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ra s\u00e2n. V\u1edbi Modric \u1edf Real, Kovac c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tiet-lo-max-allegri-da-tu-choi-real-madrid-mua-he-nay-184-194164.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\">Thibaut Courtois CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-chelsea-muon-duoc-kovacic-tu-real-172-194124.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d Kovacic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chieu-mo-kovacic-bai-toan-kho-danh-cho-sarri-172-194118.html\">Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kovacic: HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-courtois-toi-real-madrid-172-194113.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2204","checkdouble":"194189"},{"date":"17:20 10/08","title":"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 HLV Emery c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/4-van-de-hlv-emery-can-giai-quyet-truoc-mua-giai-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal 2018 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n HLV Unai Emery c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leno hay Petr Cech s\u1ebd b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Petr Cech \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i m\u1eafc t\u1edbi 6 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. G\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1982.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal 2018 Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal 2018 Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Doi-hinh-Arsenal-2018-Nhung-van-de-Mourinho-can-giai-quyet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u1eefa Cech v\u00e0 Leno kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi HLV Emery</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi C\u1ed9ng H\u00f2a S\u00e9c c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ra v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, anh c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadm. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 36 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Arsenal ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 48 b\u00e0n thua.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18, Arsenal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua nh\u1ea5t trong Top 7. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Cech l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i mua Leno t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 19,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, anh c\u00f9ng Bayer Leverkusen nh\u1eadn 40 b\u00e0n thua \u1edf Bundesliga 2017/18. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 10 tr\u1eadn, \u00edt h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Petr Cech \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i (11).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, Leno c\u00f2n m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal, anh v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 Cech v\u00e0 Leno \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai s\u1ebd b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Aubameyang v\u00e0 Lacazette</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Pierre Emerick Aubamayang, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u00a0Gabon thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Alexandre Lacazette. HLV Wenger \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a hai trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 HLV Emery c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 HLV Emery c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/4-van-de-HLV-Emery-can-giai-quyet-truoc-mua-giai-201819-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lacazette v\u00e0 Auybameyang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 Aubameyang ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh, anh ch\u01a1i l\u1ec7ch h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eafm cho Lacazette. S\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng gi\u1eefa hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Arsenal mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 m\u1edbi, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi. Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang v\u00e0 Lacazette, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Wenger \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u1edf cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o song song, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Lacazette \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn c\u00f2n Aubameyang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5 t\u00e2n binh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song Arsenal c\u0169ng chia tay Lucas Perez, Santi Cazorla, Jack Wilshere, Calum Chambers v\u00e0 Per Mertesacker. Trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, Danny Welbeck, David Ospina ho\u1eb7c Laurent Koscielny c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matteo Geundouzi co tiem nang kha lon\" title=\"Matteo Geundouzi c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/tre.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Matteo Geundouzi c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal 2018 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Matteo Geundouzi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Arsenal c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Ashely Maitland-Niles, Emile Smith-Rowe, Rob Holding, Konstantinos Mavropanos...</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, HLV Emery c\u1ea7n l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Laurent Koscielny ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 10 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Per Mertesacker \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay s\u00e2n Emirates. HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Sokratis t\u1eeb Dortmund v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17,6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sokratis Arsenal\" title=\"Sokratis Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/sokratis-noi-ve-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sokratis ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb khi t\u1edbi Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu H\u00e8 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Ngay c\u1ea3 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 8-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Borehamwood, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund v\u1eabn \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i duy nh\u1ea5t Shkodran Mustafi l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. HLV Emery s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Sokratis ho\u1eb7c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Rob Holding ho\u1eb7c Konstantinos Mavropanos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi Sokratis, Holding v\u00e0 Konstantinos Mavropanos kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. M\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Mustafi \u0111\u1ec3 Sokratis c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2203","checkdouble":"194192"},{"date":"17:33 10/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 10/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/chuyen-nhuong-barca-hot-nhat-ngay-1008.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 10/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Thomas Vermaelen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1008 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1008 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-1008-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Thomas Vermaelen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCrystal Palace \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Thomas Vermaelen, song Barca kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andre Gomes t\u1edbi Everton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 m\u00f9a, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 2.25 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-bom-xit-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-194141.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-bom-xit-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-bom-xit-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-194141.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Bom x\u1ecbt Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span><br>\r\nAndre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 m\u00f9a, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 2.25 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mina ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park. Barca \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 30,2 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Ligue 1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alba cho MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Jordi Alba\" title=\"hau ve Jordi Alba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-88,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Jordi Alba cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Star \u0111\u01b0a tin Man United \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Jordi Alba \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho Luke Shaw, song Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barcelona th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n &ldquo;d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u1ea1ng sang&rdquo; \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Blaugrana mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 Marc-Andre ter Stegen.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jasper Cillessen\" title=\"Jasper Cillessen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/HLV-Valverde-muon-Cillessen-o-lai-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Jasper Cillessen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Paul Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 v\u1eabn quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi t\u1edbi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2202","checkdouble":"194195"},{"date":"10:13 10/08","title":"H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Ai b\u1ea3o M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c mua s\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a fan M.U th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1eebng. M\u1ed7i khi h\u00e8 v\u1ec1, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u run s\u1ee3.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1ec1&hellip; photoshop<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 3 t\u00e2n binh Fred, Lee Grant v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot &ndash; 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m d\u00e0y b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Jose Mourinho li\u00ean t\u1ee5c than v\u00e3n v\u00e0 ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 m\u00f9a h\u00e8, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t k\u00eau g\u00e0o CLB mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb l\u1edbn t\u1edbi nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u00f4ng. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ec3 ra nh\u1eefng Harry Maguire, Toby Alderweireld, Diego Godin, Jerome Boateng, Yerry Mina hay k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Kurt Zouma &ndash; h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng Ivan Perisic hay Gareth Bale \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Sau c\u00f9ng, nh\u1eefng n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n tr\u00ean tr\u00e1n Mourinho ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng d\u00e0y h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111ang nh\u00ecn danh s\u00e1ch tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U m\u00e0 c\u00e1c fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ea1o ra v\u1edbi \u00e1nh m\u1eaft ao \u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/8.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/9.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Gareth Bale c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/11.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sao tr\u1ebb Pulisic c\u1ee7a Dortmund</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Arnautovic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n