able style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/12.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, PCT Ed Woodward th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i h\u01a1n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-hay-ngung-than-van-va-chung-to-ban-than-172-194158.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/mourinho-hay-ngung-than-van-va-chung-to-ban-than.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-hay-ngung-than-van-va-chung-to-ban-than-172-194158.html\">Mourinho h\u00e3y ng\u1eebng than v\u00e3n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Tottenham l\u00e0 Tim Sherwood cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean than v\u00e3n v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho Man United.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-top-10-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-premier-league-172-194156.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/day-top-10-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-premier-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-top-10-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-premier-league-172-194156.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Top 10 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t Premier League</span><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 9/8. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Top 10 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t Premier League m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2201","checkdouble":"194160"},{"date":"10:30 10/08","title":"C\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/cac-muc-tieu-tu-choi-mu-la-loi-cua-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Tottenham ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 bao, M.U g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U b\u1ecb C\u0110V ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 trung v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u1eeda t\u00e1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecd li\u00ean h\u1ec7. Trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00f4i k\u00e9o Diego Godin &ndash; m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1eefng Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire, Jerome Boateng v\u00e0 Yerry Mina \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi M.U, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a BL\u0110, hay ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 b\u1edfi Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 M.U tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter:<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@SiisiKwesi: </strong></em>&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 t\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@DeanJones:</strong> </em>&ldquo;R\u1ea5t th\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Godin gia nh\u1eadp Old Trafford, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@truene:</strong></em> &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y (Diego Godin). C\u1ee9 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Phil Jones m\u00e0 xem.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<em>&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@ekupnse:</strong></em><strong> </strong>&ldquo;Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u00e0o c\u1ea5u Godin trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. CLB c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8\" title=\"Godin t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-108-mourinho-dien-tiet-vi-bi-phia-godin-loi-dung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Godin t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em><strong>@m16cam:</strong></em> &ldquo;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t ai \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@adedayoice:</strong></em> &ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U. Chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra v\u1eady?&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>@Bjohnson: </em></strong>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta b\u1ecb c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u1edfi Mourinho. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00f4ng ta ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. M.U c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay-172-194160.html\"><img 