Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 mua s\u1eafm t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Spurs \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eafn nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/HLV-Pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Mauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n r\u1ea7u d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0o. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh&rdquo;, Pochettino n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 25 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Man United hay Man City. Nh\u01b0ng trong nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 CLB \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h30 ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 7 t\u1edbi (11/8), Tottenham s\u1ebd ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a 2018/19. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean Newcastle c\u1ee7a HLV Rafa Benitez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Tottenham tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-tottenham-truoc-mua-giai-201819-nguy-co-vang-khoi-top-4-172-194053.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: Nguy c\u01a1 v\u0103ng kh\u1ecfi Top 4</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-tottenham-he-2018-172-194040.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00e8 2018: Mua kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i, b\u00e1n ch\u1eb3ng xong!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-that-vong-voi-world-cup-2018-172-193953.html\">Gi\u00e0nh Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng, Harry Kane v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-cho-tottenham-172-193924.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t, Pochettino v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2199","checkdouble":"194162"},{"date":"10:32 10/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Valenciennes vs Chateauroux 01h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-valenciennes-vs-chateauroux-01h00-ngay-118-hang-2-phap-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Valenciennes vs Chateauroux l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 3 gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p Ligue 2 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Valenciennes vs Chateauroux 01h00 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Valenciennes vs Chateauroux 01h00 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Valenciennes-vs-Chateauroux.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Valenciennes vs Chateauroux</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Valenciennes vs Chateauroux</span></span></span></span></span></span>: 0-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng 2 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng \u1edf cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Chateauroux t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Valenciennes l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 Valenciennes l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7n nh\u1edb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau 19 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng Chateauroux l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 8/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Ri\u00eang tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam 1 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o Chateauroux ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m s\u00e0o huy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Valenciennes. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jean-Luc Vasseur \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng sau 4 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Valenciennes ch\u01a1i t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chateauroux b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n thua sau 4 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n* 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Valenciennes \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, trong khi Chateauroux ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 1 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n* Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong s\u1ed1 3 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Valenciennes l\u1ea1i thua 2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chateauroux.<br>\r\n* 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp Chateauroux tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Valenciennes th\u1eafng 2, thua 1.<br>\r\n* L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Valenciennes, Chateauroux \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2-1.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2198","checkdouble":"194163"},{"date":"11:04 10/08","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/tiet-lo-max-allegri-da-tu-choi-real-madrid-mua-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin HLV Allegri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Allegri n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV c\u1ee7a Real l\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Julen Lopetegui th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n qu\u1ed1c&rdquo;, khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c trong khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t HLV kh\u00e1c llaijtwf ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Zidane, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Max Allegri c\u1ee7a Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB th\u00e0nh Turin. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, Allegri ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00ec cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi ng\u00e0i Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u1edbi Juventus khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 cho m\u1ecdi HLV. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Allegri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid\" title=\"HLV Allegri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/tiet-lo-max-allegri-da-tu-choi-real-madrid-mua-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Allegri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t &lsquo;bandiera&rsquo; (bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh) nh\u01b0 Buffon hay Del Piero? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, hay mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi vi\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed cho Juve, trong khi t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m&rdquo; &ndash; Allegri k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin, Los Blancos c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t lu\u00f4n Cris Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 115 tri\u1ec7u euro. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Juve, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Allegri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, khi \u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi CR7 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\">Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft \u1edf Real, Marcelo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi-176-194082.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi-176-194082.html\">Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Juve \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nBom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Juventus m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Douglas Costa ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2197","checkdouble":"194164"}]}